<p><b>Biblical inerrancy</b> is the doctrinal position that in its original form, the <a href="/wiki/Bible" title="Bible">Bible</a> is totally without error, and free from all contradiction; "referring to the complete accuracy of Scripture, including the historical and scientific parts."<sup id="cite_ref-inerrancy_0-0" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-inerrancy-0" title=""><span>[</span>1<span>]</span></a></sup></p>
